reaction.Name: Two FPP molecules dimerize to form presqualene diphosphate
Condensation of acetyl CoA with acetoacetyl CoA to form HMG-CoA
Reduction of presqualene diphosphate to form squalene
Squalene is oxidized to its epoxide
Cholesta-724-dien-3beta-ol is desaturated to form cholesta-5724-trien-3beta-ol
Isopentenyl pyrophosphate rearranges to dimethylallyl pyrophosphate
Addition of isopentenyl pyrophosphate to DMAPP
Another isopentenyl pyrophosphate is added to geranyl pyrophosphate
